rior flow, with\nstructures consistent with features from plane Poiseuille and Rayleigh-B\\'enard\nflows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Aug 2017 19:38:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-01"}
