astically from that\nin quiescent water, and depends strongly on Froude number and direction of\nmotion. For Froude numbers typical of such boats, wave resistance can vary by a\nfactor 3 between upstream and downstream motion, and the strong Froude number\ndependence is made more complicated by interference effects. The lateral\nradiation force ... [abstract truncated due to ArXiV's space restrictions]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2017 07:53:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-09"}
